values: it feels like a lfie time in this past week. alot has happened good, and not so good. i finally got to see him. the best concert i have ever seen, and i got enjoy it with the best person ive met in a long time. also i had the scare of my life. it was a good and bad thing i guess. but i dont really want to get into that.

Time had been flying by. Its already mid october, and summer seems so far away. i love this time of year, normaly im planning a quiet boarding trip solo. or just waiting around for the great time to buy shit holiday. but this year is so much diffrent. she loves thi time of year and i will make the best of it. we are going to see ville valo on the 21st and i am at a loss for words on how to describe my feelings on that subject. other than that its random fun hay rides VNV Murphy bitches lol. we shall see what is to come. all i know is that im in love and feeling like 10000000 dollars right now. shes smart beautiful sexy and fun in so many ways. hopefully moving to prvidence with the cew sooner than later. moving to a new place with erock this week. im excited just to have my own room again. i have high hopes for the future to come. on another note.....take care and feel better baby i love you!

good times and good people. life is a funny little bitch. right when you think your down and out and there isnt much hope left someone comes along to show you the way. make all your worries about yourself, and who you are fade. showing you that true happiness is in the mirror. im floating and i never want to touch the ground again. dont give up on hope, life, or yourself. there is someone and somthing out there for everyone. in the words of a poet "Love life".

nothing could compare. wandering throught this world blinded by flase happiness, and you cure me. im tortured with the past yet you make the future seem so bright. im infatuated, im crazy, im losing it all for you....

where to begin, first this had been the most fucked up year of my life. ive lost loved ones, fallen far into a bad place. to top it off, i have nothing plesant so far and here we are nearing 2008. sometimes i guess when everything is down and out all you can hope for is more.  well these past weeks have been an eye opener that not all in life is totally bad, its what you make of it. i have met a few new people and reconsiled with a few lost friends and have been feeling alot better in some ways. i remember myself now, and the person i once was, and thats the best feeling ever. how good it feels to be back. watch out world murphy will rise again!
